      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING URBAN (4) has an excellent record here having never missed the placings in six starts, including three wins and three placings. Recorded a 8 length win (29.43) in a Grade 5 last time at Q Parklands. With a clean break looks hard to beat. ALSTON (3) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on his superb win the start prior, getting around Healesville over 300m in 16.55. Should be in this for a long way. BONNEVILLE (1) goes very well this course and distance starting eight times for three wins and two minors. In the money last time at this track (20.03) in a P5, finishing a 2 length third. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. PROFESSOR SAMSON (2) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
